{"word":"ἐσθίω/ἔσθω","slug":"ἐσθίω/ἔσθω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐσϑίω</el>/<el>ἔσϑω</el></b> [based on the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ impv.\">impv.</a> <el>ἔσϑι</el> ‘eat!’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘consume food’, <b>eat <a href='B:470 6:25'>Mt 6:25</a>; <a href='B:470 11:18'>11:18f</a>; <a href='B:480 1:6'>Mk 1:6</a>; <a href='B:490 5:30'>Lk 5:30</a>; <a href='B:490 7:33'>7:33f</a>; <a href='B:500 4:31'>J 4:31</a>; <a href='B:510 10:13'>Ac 10:13</a>; <a href='B:520 14:2'>Ro 14:2b</a>; <a href='B:530 8:7'>1 Cor 8:7</a>; <a href='B:530 9:7'>9:7</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on milk <b><a href='B:530 9:7'>9:7b</a></b>); <b><a href='B:530 11:26'>11:26</a>; <a href='B:600 3:8'>2 Th 3:8</a>.</b> By extension in remarkably forceful imagery <b><a href='B:500 6:53'>J 6:53</a>; <a href='B:730 2:7'>Rv 2:7</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> by imagistic extension to corrosive or destructive consumption <b>eat, devour, consume <a href='B:650 10:27'>Hb 10:27</a></b> (fiery zeal); <b><a href='B:660 5:3'>Js 5:3</a></b> (rust)<b>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐσθής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐσήμανα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}